[{"id":"fe3ba67969e0a78d49011ea6861ee27f","from":"Rahna Jalashgar","from_email":"rjalashgar@nysgmail.com","to":"J. Epstein","to_list":[{"name":"J. Epstein","email":"jeeproject@yahoo.com"}],"cc_list":[],"subject":"for Jeffrey","date":"2007-11-19T19:12:28.000Z","formatted_date":"Nov 19, 2007","formatted_time":"7:12 PM","body":" \n\n________________________________\n\nFrom: Simon, Laetitia [mailto:Laetitia.Simon@umusic.com] \nSent: Monday, November 19, 2007 12:19 PM\nTo: Rahna Jalashgar\nSubject: for Jeffrey\n\n\n\nHey Jeffrey\n\nHow are you?\n\nI wanted to apologize cause I've been really selfish bothering you with my problems when you have other things to deal with. You have always been a friend to me and I feel that I didn't do the same with you\n\nI sincerely hope that everything is going to work out the best for you, and know that if there is ANYTHING I can do to help I'm here!!\n\nSend me news, take care of yourself\n\nMuch love\n\nLaetitia\n\n \n\nLAETITIA SIMON\n\nAssistante de direction du label AZ\n\nUniversal Music\n\n20 rue des Foss\u00e9s Saint Jacques\n\n75005 Paris\n\nTel: 01 44 41 50 65 \n\n      06 70 45 48 55\n\nFax:01 44 41 50 60 \n\nLes coulisses du label AZ en un seul clic sur: http://rss.universalmusic.fr/podcast/AZ/ <http://rss.universalmusic.fr/podcast/AZ/> \n\n \n\n","body_html":"<!DOCTYPE HTML PUBLIC \"-//W3C//DTD HTML 4.0 Transitional//EN\">\n<HTML xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/TR/REC-html40\" xmlns:o = \n\"urn:schemas-microsoft-com:office:office\" xmlns:w = \n\"urn:schemas-microsoft-com:office:word\"><HEAD>\n<META http-equiv=Content-Type content=\"text/html; charset=iso-8859-1\">\n<META content=\"MSHTML 6.00.3790.94\" name=GENERATOR>\n<STYLE>@font-face {\n\tfont-family: Monotype Corsiva;\n}\n@page Section1 {size: 595.3pt 841.9pt; margin: 70.85pt 70.85pt 70.85pt 70.85pt; }\nP.MsoNormal {\n\tFONT-SIZE: 12pt; MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; FONT-FAMILY: \"Times New Roman\"\n}\nLI.MsoNormal {\n\tFONT-SIZE: 12pt; MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; FONT-FAMILY: \"Times New Ro